c: 3
v: 20
t: "Ne nibakhureba boola mbu; “esie ogwisiye obweni bwanje ukhuhenga Nyasaye nende balia abanonda.’’ Ne boolela balia bahebwa eshitabu nende timbiti mbu- “Musilimile?” nenibasilimile awomanabamalileokhulunjikha. Ne nibakhaya, ewe olisa wokhusia uburume, Ne Nyasaye alolanga muno Abasumba bebe"